Quickstrike:





Quickstrike picked Stingtra. "Don't be crazy now. Come on." He walked into 
the Predacon cave. He didn't understand her behavior. It almost scared him. 
He had never seen a female act like this before. He made his way to the CR 
tank.

"We need t' talk," he firmly said before he put her on the platform.
